Class FIARLearnerState

java.lang.Object
  fiarautoplayer.FIARLearnerState

public class FIARLearnerState
extends java.lang.Object

Represents the state of the learning process It holds the values of the learning parameters, number of simulated games used in the learning process and the learned weights of the function approximators
